# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CoffeeManager-OS — .gitignore
# This repo is not yet under git. This file exists so that WHEN `git init` is
# first run, live secrets and local state are never swept into a commit.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Secrets — NEVER commit ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Real credentials live here (Telegram token, OpenClaw/Anthropic key, Google
# refresh token, Smart-ID personal code). Commit settings.env.example instead.
config/settings.env
config/settings.env.local
*.env
!*.env.example

# ── Virtual environments ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.venv/
.venv-*/
venv/
env/

# ── Local database & runtime state ──────────────────────────────────────────
# memory.sqlite* covers the DB and its -journal/-wal/-shm sidecars; *.bak covers
# the timestamped snapshots reset_barista_data.py writes — full copies of the
# compliance DB including employee personal data. NEVER commit any of these.
python/data/memory.sqlite*
python/data/*.bak
python/data/pl_draft_*.json
python/data/workspace/manual_review/
# Defense in depth: ANY SQLite DB or .bak snapshot anywhere in the tree (e.g. a
# manual `copy memory.sqlite memory.sqlite.bak` landing at python/, not data/).
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-journal
*.sqlite-wal
*.sqlite-shm
*.bak

# ── Python caches ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# ── Editor / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ── Local tooling binaries (downloaded, not project source) ─────────────────
cloudflared.exe
*.exe
